ta LC \u2014 \u2014 \u22641 \uf0fb \u2014 \u2014 \u22641 \uf0fb Zannichellia palustris LC \u2014 \u2014 1-3 \uf0fb \u2014 \u2014 \uf0fb \uf0fb Glyceria spicata DD \u2014 \u2014 \uf0fb \uf0fb \u2014 \u2014 \uf0fb \u22641 Bolboschoenus planiculmis NE \u2014 \u2014 \uf0fb \uf0fb \u2014 \u2014 \uf0fb 1-3 Cladophora glomerata NE \u2014 \u2014 20 \uf0fb \u2014 \u2014 \uf0fb \uf0fb Dorycnium rectum NE \u2014 \u2014 \uf0fb \u22641 \u2014 \u2014 \uf0fb \uf0fb Hildenbrandia rivularis NE \u2014 \u2014 \uf0fb 1-3 \u2014 \u2014 \uf0fb \uf0fb Holoschoenus vulgaris NE \u2014 \u2014 \uf0fb 1-3 \u2014 \u2014 15 \uf0fb Hypericum tomentosum NE \u2014 \u2014 \uf0fb \u22641 \u2014 \u2014 \uf0fb \uf0fb Sium latifoium NE \u2014 \u2014 \uf0fb \uf0fb \u2014 \u2014 3-5 \uf0fb Bacillariophyceae sp. \u2014 \u2014 40 \uf0fb \u2014 \u2014 \uf0fb \uf0fb Cinclidotus sp. \u2014 \u2014 1-3 \uf0fb \u2014 \u2014 \uf0fb \uf0fb Glyceria sp. \u2014 \u2014 \u22641 \uf0fb \u2014 \u2014 \uf0fb \uf0fb Juncus sp.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "b5d90c37-7706-4567-b143-5b7053bf94a4": {"__data__": {"id_": "b5d90c37-7706-4567-b143-5b7053bf94a4", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/resources/grey-literature/conservation-status-freshwater-species-and-habitats-key-biodiversity", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "The conservation status of freshwater species and habitats in Key Biodiversity Areas at the Sebou river basin", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/resources/grey-literature/conservation-status-freshwater-species-and-habitats-key-biodiversity", "Author": "International Union for Conservat