on de savane arbustive\uf03c 3.3. Le Massif du Fouta Djalon Figure 5 : Carte de localisation du Massif du Fouta Djalon et de distribution des \u00e9cosyst\u00e8mes. Source : WASCAL 8 Le bassin versant du Mono situ\u00e9 dans la r\u00e9gion du golfe de Guin\u00e9e, est partag\u00e9 entre le B\u00e9nin et le Togo. Les parties hautes et moyennes du bassin sont en grande partie sur le territoire togolais (Figure 6). Il a une superficie de 24 110,83 km2 \u00e0 l\u2019exutoire de Kpondave et s\u2019\u00e9tend sur 560 km du Nord au Sud et plus pr\u00e9cis\u00e9ment entre 06\u00b016\u2019 et 09\u00b020\u2019N et 0\u00b042\u2019", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "104b81ff-36c2-443a-a989-ca43225f6597": {"__data__": {"id_": "104b81ff-36c2-443a-a989-ca43225f6597", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/resources/grey-literature/mediterranean-programme-iucn-centre-mediterranean-cooperation-2021-2024", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Mediterranean Programme of IUCN Centre for Mediterranean Cooperation 2021 \u2013 2024", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/resources/grey-literature/mediterranean-programme-iucn-centre-mediterranean-cooperation-2021-2024", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "5c6672d6d5d83fa9a55f529624aa91918a113f2a96fe011042dfc17852df4367"}, "3": {"node_id": "5375c4a0-0b45-4e8d-a853-24bc69f6adb9", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/resources/grey-literature/mediterranean-programme-iucn-centre-mediterranean-